+ `second_name` (string, required) - identifier
+ `birth_date` (string, required) - identifier
+ `tax_id` (string, required) - identifier
+ `phone_number` (string, required) - identifier
+ `birth_certificate` (string, required) - identifier
+ `birth_place` (string, required) - identifier
+ `page` (string, required) - identifier
+ `page_size` (string, required) - identifier

+ Request (application/json)
+ Headers
Authorization: Bearer c2778f3064753ea70de870a53795f5c9
X-Custom-PSK: a2aa05c76f3f2d91870f923a53cc8aa8f23bbc01a8238d1c2c26d4299715a7e4

+ Response 200 (application/json)
+ Attributes (Response__Process_OK)

+ data (array)
    + (object)
        + include Person_Short
        + merged_persons (array, required)
            + (object)
                + id (string) - 57e30ea3-16f1-4f8e-adcd-1a05e99e2d22 - identifier of the relation of persons who are compared during the deduplication process
                + inserted_at (string) - 2019-05-08T15:34:00Z

                + merge_person_id (string) - bdadc2a7-7283-4f24-bc99-8d8d9808af80 - identifier of a person who is recognized as a duplicate and subsequently deactivated
                + person_id (string) - b075f148-7f93-4fc2-b2ec-2d81b19a9b7b - identifier of the person who as a result of the deduplication is recognized as true and subsequently left active
                + updated_at (string) - 2019-05-08T15:34:00Z

+ Response 403 (application/json)
+ Attributes (Response_Error)

+ meta (Response__Meta)
    + code (number) - 403
+ error (Response__Error)
    + type: too_many_results
    + message (string) - This API method returns only exact match results, please retry with more specific search result

