        + id (string) - b075f148-7f93-4fc2-b2ec-2d81b19a9b7b - Medication Dispense Response Identifier
        + medication_request (object) - Medication request
            + include Medication_request_Public_Response
        + dispensed_at (string) - 2017-08-17 - date of dispense
